[I] Aurorae is a themeable window decoration for KWin

[T] Aurorae is a themeable window decoration for KWin. It supports theme files
[T] consisting of several SVG files for decoration and buttons. Themes can be
[T] installed and selected directly in the configuration module of KWin
[T] decorations.

[U] https://www.kde.org

